== Classical Military Music "Kishimai" == '''Kishimai''' is also the title of a {{ill|wind band|ja|吹奏楽|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/wind band|qq=}} composition by [[:en:Akira Ifukube|Akira Ifukube]], best known for his work on [[:en:Godzilla (franchise)|Godzilla]]. Composed in [[:en:1943|Showa 18]][[Category:Years needing redirect replacements]] at the request of the [[:en:Imperial Japanese Navy|Imperial Japanese Navy]], the piece was completed in February of that year and premiered on April 8 under the baton of {{ill|Itsurō Hattori|ja|服部逸郎|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itsurō Hattori|qq=}}, performed by the Tokyo Broadcast Wind Orchestra on NHK Radio.
