The term {{ill|Kishi|ja|吉師|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kishi|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 吉士|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 吉士}} refers to clans involved in diplomacy and naval activities during the Yamato court era. Many of these clans were of foreign origin and were associated with the Abe clan.
